        "fc-eyebrow": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Case study</p>",
            "size": "sm",
            "uppercase": true,
            "muted": true,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "fc-heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Orion Quarterly — a redesign that earned its keep.",
            "size": "4xl",
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "fc-body-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Orion came to us with a circulation slide and an identity that hadn't been touched in nine years. The brief was a light refresh. What we proposed was a full editorial rebuild — new masthead, new type system, new grid, new photography direction.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "fc-body-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Twelve weeks later the first issue landed. Subscriptions rose 34% across two quarters. Editorial won two industry awards the following year. More importantly, the magazine reads like itself again.</p>",
            "size": "base",
            "uppercase": false,
            "muted": false,
            "position": "right"
          }
        },
        "fc-button": {
          "type": "button",
          "settings": {
            "link": {
              "text": "Read the full study",
              "href": "contact.html",
              "target": "_self"
            },
            "style": "secondary",
            "size": "medium",
            "alignment": "start",
            "position": "right"
          }
        }
      },
      "blocksOrder": [
